{"tid":1783502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[全支攬抄] 內地「炒豬團」放非洲豬瘟病毒牟暴利 港豬農：今年做冬要捱貴豬","createTime":"2019-12-15T01:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T06:28:57.000Z","uid":303462,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bedddef6f3c136aeae9422d662af52fe07a024dd","tid":1783502,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"下周就是冬至（22/12），豬肉價格有升無跌，本地市民可能要捱貴豬「過冬」！內地近日公佈11月居民消費價格指數（CPI）按年升4.5%，創8年以來新高，當中受到非洲豬瘟疫情影響，豬肉價格上升1.1倍。中國官方期刊《半月談》報道，不法商人組成「炒豬團」，以非法手段抬高豬價，從中牟取暴利，並向養殖場、養殖戶的豬群邊丟棄死豬，或投放帶有非洲豬瘟病毒的飼料，然後散佈疫情消息，壓低活豬收購價。本地豬農接受《蘋果》訪問時不諱言，這些情況一直在內地出現，在國內經營豬場的業內人士都遇過「炒豬團」，「<strong>專登放非洲豬瘟入去農場，整到啲豬全部死晒</strong>，佢哋咪可以好平咁收晒啲豬走囉」。<br />\n<br />\n非洲豬瘟在內地爆發以來，各地一邊加強疫情防控，限制生豬非法跨省調運，一邊加大調控力度，平抑市場上上漲的豬肉價格，但一些不法商人為了牟取暴利，不顧政府禁令組成「炒豬團」，跨省收豬、賣豬、炒豬，而不管當中有沒有病豬。為了偷運生豬，有的買通監管人員，偽造手續證明；為了壓價收豬，有的散播疫情謠言，製造社會恐慌情緒，甚至向他人飼養的豬群投放非洲豬瘟病毒。<br />\n<br />\n本地豬農品牌「香港家豬」負責人劉漢傑向《蘋果》坦言，內地非洲豬瘟的疫情一直沒有減退迹象，內地供港的活豬供應也大受影響，平均每日大約1,500隻活豬輸港，<strong>港府也沒有放寬本地豬農增加飼養豬隻</strong>，估計今年冬至都要捱貴豬，但本地豬農則不會趁勢加價，「只係賣番未有非洲豬瘟嘅價錢，因為一路以嚟本地豬都係比大陸豬貴兩三成」。劉漢傑估計，今年做冬的本地豬瘦肉一般為60至70港元一斤，排骨為80至90港元一斤。<br />\n<br />\n【豬肉黃金價】內地「炒豬團」放非洲豬瘟病毒牟暴利 港豬農：今年做冬要捱貴豬<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191215&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60373628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191215%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60373628&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=dabc1d7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191215%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60373628&h=9f323b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191215&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60373628</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444f6f690a93b28b224725869da4694b3f140416","tid":1783502,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"10013c69a05e0642f243c45587c29bc7b7b5e3da","tid":1783502,"uid":331421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"控制唔到瘟疫，就屈係人為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd761d57a8d25ccc61a7079b5aa72acf89ca7ac","tid":1783502,"uid":55413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"a7a1904c96f4fa75f399aac2a3be621ad893c448","tid":1783502,"uid":103521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"10013c69a05e0642f243c45587c29bc7b7b5e3da","tid":1783502,"uid":331421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"控制唔到瘟疫，就屈係人為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"why not both, 支那冇人性"},{"pid":"6f59f02d32692d2e611b6a290db49b140db0dd8c","tid":1783502,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6182dec94bef946f7c31dee744d87a6f34ac9e","tid":1783502,"uid":98163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T01:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔